gov.nasa.jpf

Class CachedROHttpConnection

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.net.URLConnection
      • java.net.HttpURLConnection
        • gov.nasa.jpf.CachedROHttpConnection

  • public class CachedROHttpConnection
extends HttpURLConnection
    this is just a very rough abstraction at this point, which only supports reading static URL contents. The data is cached for subsequent access, to avoid DOS by means of model checking
